ABOUT THE COURSE:


In this course, I learnt best practices for how to use data analytics to make any company more competitive and more profitable. I was also introduced to the most critical business metrics and distinguish them from mere data.
 
The course gave me a clear picture of the vital but different roles business analysts, business data analysts, and data scientists each play in various types of companies. I came to know exactly what skills are required to be hired for, and succeed at, these high-demand jobs.
 
Finally, I was able to use a checklist provided in the course to score any company on how effectively it is embracing big data culture. Digital companies like Amazon, Uber and Airbnb are transforming entire industries through their creative use of big data. I undeerstood  why these companies are so disruptive and how they use data-analytics techniques to out-compete traditional companies.

SKILLS GAINED:
1.Data Analysis
2.Business Analysis
3.Business Analytics
4.Business Process
